definition: to teach classes in addition to other duties/to hold several teaching jobs
double/twice/simultaneous/holding two or more (official) posts at the same time

sentences.english: He is a professor who gives lectures in several universities this semester.
sentences.chinese: 它是教授，這學期在幾所大學兼課句號。

sentences.english: Mr. Cook teaches part-time in our school.
sentences.chinese: 庫克先生在我們學校兼課。
